caption:
Just a small glimpse into my camera roll😅 This #MentalHealthAwarenessMonth I want to thank Jane and Rems for being a constant support in my life and being there for me in every moment. Their goofiness and silly personalities brighten every single day and no matter what I accomplish in the pool, they just know me as “dad”. 
 
Together with @NuloPetFood, I invite you to take a moment today to thank your pet for all the comfort and support they give you by posting an incredible moment you’ve shared with them (or a silly picture of your pet)! Use the hashtag #TheyFuelUs and tag @nulopetfood for a chance to be featured on Nulo’s social media. 
 
#FuelIncredible #NuloPartner
